general.gigTitle: design and develop your website with webflow

sellerCard.oneLiner: Hard working youngster that loves design
sellerCard.description:
I'm a young freelancer who's passionate about animating and creating visually stunning websites.

My youth and energy allow me to stay on top of the latest trends and technologies.

Let's bring your vision to life!

description.content:
Please contact me before placing an order.


I have worked on a lot of Webflow projects that grab people's attention. I focus on creating minimalistic and easy to use websites that your customers will love. Elevate your online presence with a hand-crafted website.



What I offer:

  • Fully responsive Website tailored to your needs.
  • SEO optimization
  • Design development (Figma, XD, Sketch etc)
  • Design or redesign of your current Website


Your advantages:

  1. EASY to update. Yes, even by you or your team, no coding required.
  2. SEO Optimized designed to attract traffic.
  3. PRACTICAL and elegant. Easy to use layout, loved by visitors.
  4. Speed optimization. Loads quickly for a smooth user experience.
  5. Assistance: Beyond delivery, I offer 15 days of dedicated support.
  6. Works Everywhere: Converts on any device phone, tablet, or desktop.



How it works


Initializing - We work together on the look and feel, then I bring it to life using Webflow.


Finishing - Once your project is built, we'll check everything and handle hosting, so your new site will be fully functional and ready to go!


Check out some of my previous work here

https://www.vision-web.online/


Ready to level up your website? Let's make it happen!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you build a NEW website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can help you bring your ideas to life from scratch. I focus on creating SEO Friendly and Mobile Responsive websites so you don't have to worry about a thing.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer support after completing the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I do. After completing the project I will show you how to manage your website yourself. I will ofer you tips on how to track your website performance.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: In order to get started with the website I will need: Information content, your branding assets, design reference (if there is a preference) and any other important files.

reviews.comment:
Cristian was incredible to work with. He was responsive despite big gap in time zones (I am in US pacific time). 

He provided iterations on the project quickly, was receptive to feedback and did a nice job clarifying ambiguities in the instructions I provided. Will definitely be working with him again on the next project.

Cristian did an OUTSTANDING job on our website! His professionalism and attention to detail are top-notch. Working with him was seamless, thanks to his language fluency, deep understanding of our needs, and timely delivery. Highly recommend! 👍
Great working with Cristian. Good eye for creativity, neatness and gets the job done quickly.
I had no idea about the design, and oh my God! it is fantastic! great work Cristian, I love it!

Cristian did a really great job. We had a very short time frame and he not only managed to deliver in time, he also exceeded the expectations. After the project was delivered he was still available for questions and small fixes.

Thank You Cristian
